text.tspan: t's nine o'clock, and Little Timmy is happily asleep, unaware that there are monsters under his bed -
drooling, tentacled, hairy THINGS that wait in the shadows. Will he make it through the night? Or will he make a tasty snack for some eldritch creature? Only you can
keep him safe until the sun rises.

g.text: Stop the monsters by clicking on them.
